{
  "_doc": [
    "Default mcpServers catalog for zelosMCP. Trimmed in PR 7 to the",
    "minimum useful set: kubernetes + docker (stdio, no auth) and one",
    "github passthrough backend referencing the github_oauth_app",
    "provider in configs/auth-providers.json.",
    "",
    "The github backend's wrappers are GATED behind successful auth via",
    "the GUI Connections page (left nav -> Authentication -> Connections).",
    "Until the user authorizes, Cursor sees no github__* tools at all.",
    "",
    "For the broader Nike/atlassian/artifactory/box example matrix, see",
    "configs/example-passthrough-zelosmcp.json + configs/example-auth-",
    "providers.json — load both with:",
    "  make load ZELOSMCP_CONFIG=configs/example-passthrough-zelosmcp.json \\",
    "             ZELOSMCP_AUTH_PROVIDERS_FILE=configs/example-auth-providers.json"
  ],
  "builtin": {
    "response_format": "compact_json",
    "compress": {
      "level": "low"
    }
  },
  "mcpServers": {
    "kubernetes": {
      "command": "npx",
      "args": [
        "-y",
        "kubernetes-mcp-server@latest"
      ],
      "started": false,
      "compress": {
        "level": "medium"
      }
    },
    "docker": {
      "command": "uvx",
      "args": [
        "mcp-server-docker"
      ],
      "env": {
        "DOCKER_HOST": "unix:///var/run/docker.sock"
      }
    },
    "github": {
      "type": "streamable-http",
      "url": "https://api.githubcopilot.com/mcp/",
      "passthrough": true,
      "started": false,
      "auth": {
        "provider": "github_oauth_app"
      }
    },
    "filesystem": {
      "command": "npx",
      "args": [
        "-y",
        "@modelcontextprotocol/server-filesystem",
        "/user_data_rw"
      ],
      "started": false,
      "compress": {
        "level": "medium"
      }
    },
    "mcpdoc": {
      "command": "uvx",
      "args": [
        "--from", "mcpdoc", "mcpdoc",
        "--urls",
        "MCP:https://modelcontextprotocol.io/llms.txt",
        "Anthropic:https://docs.anthropic.com/llms.txt",
        "--transport", "stdio"
      ],
      "started": false,
      "compress": {
        "level": "low"
      }
    }
  }
}
